5
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:57,881
[SPEAKER_11]: 10th regular meeting Medford City Council May 26th 2026 is called order.

6
00:01:57,921 --> 00:01:59,281
[SPEAKER_11]: Mr. Clerk please call the roll.

7
00:01:59,301 --> 00:02:04,202
[SPEAKER_08]: Thank you.

