00:35:02,125 --> 00:35:13,432
[SPEAKER_11]: The Community Development Board did meet on this but there has been a hiccup in regards to the total development cost metric because the state is no longer putting out the total development cost metric.

440
00:35:13,872 --> 00:35:22,937
[SPEAKER_11]: So I'm going to open the public hearing and there's been a request from Planning Development and Sustainability that we extend the public hearing, continue the public hearing to July 14th.

