443
00:35:31,695 --> 00:35:32,855
[SPEAKER_11]: Fractional hearing.

444
00:35:33,195 --> 00:35:36,076
[SPEAKER_11]: Fractional, the fractional units.

445
00:35:36,476 --> 00:35:48,859
[SPEAKER_19]: Yeah, so basically the status update is that the benchmark that we were using to set the price for the value of an affordable unit was monitored by the state, the QAP Qualified Allocation Plan.

446
00:35:49,399 --> 00:35:55,021
[SPEAKER_19]: And it turns out, we just found out, the state is no longer updating that on a regular process or standard timeline.

447
