449
00:35:58,642 --> 00:36:01,524
[SPEAKER_19]: So therefore it will not be a good benchmark to use.

450
00:36:01,664 --> 00:36:06,407
[SPEAKER_19]: So we're just evaluating new options for how we determine what that value should be.

451
00:36:06,467 --> 00:36:07,947
