549
00:43:16,887 --> 00:43:22,111
[SPEAKER_19]: Just through the chair, as a clarification, what kind of information would be helpful?

550
00:43:23,912 --> 00:43:24,932
[SPEAKER_07]: Honestly, it's nothing.

551
00:43:24,952 --> 00:43:26,974
[SPEAKER_07]: We've been asking for financial information.

552
