[SPEAKER_11]: I think it's less about specifically the Affordable Housing Trust.

553
00:43:30,176 --> 00:43:40,743
[SPEAKER_07]: And if it would, that's a great, I apologize, but if we could hold that off until we get our information, because I don't want to say no to this, but unfortunately it's coming before

