821
01:03:12,782 --> 01:03:15,223
[SPEAKER_03]: How would that kind of figure itself out?

822
01:03:15,263 --> 01:03:21,666
[SPEAKER_03]: So I don't know if that's something here to answer those questions or to look at it at committee, just to kind of flesh some of that out in there.

